name: guangzhou F&J leather co.,ltd
overview: F&J leather co.,ltd is a professional bag manufacturer, an experienced trading company as well as a reliable agent located in guangzhou, China.With 10 years’ experience in bag products, we have our own production base with advanced production equipment and professional workforce of technicians and engineers. We are specialized in producing all kinds of bags, likes ladies’ bag, fashion backpack, hobo bag, shoulder bags, tote bag, cosmetic bag, shopping bag, evening bag, wallet and other related products for worldwide customers. We also supply OEM services as per your requirements and create samples of all kinds of bags.In addition, we also act as a trading company and agent here in order to take advantage of the worldwide famous commodity city so as to make our customers feel easy when they need various types of goods for their markets.Adhering to the credo of “Sincerity and Credit”, we always supply products with “Competitive Prices, Excellent Quality and Quick Shipment” and provide perfect services for clients in the whole process.Please don’t hesitate to contact us with any question you may have. We sincerely look forward to hearing from you and giving you the best answer as soon as possible.We warmly welcome friends from all over the world to communicate and negotiate and wish friendly long-term business relationships with you in the near future
